OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMore strikes planned as    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fteachers reject pay offer  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Teachers in England will strike on     
OL,6, Thursday 27 April and Tuesday 2 May    
OL,7, after members of the UK's largest      
OL,8, education union rejected a pay offer.  
OL,10,FTeachers were offered a #1,000 one-off 
OL,11,Fpayment this year, and a 4.3% rise next
OL,12,Fyear. Starting salaries would also rise
OL,13,Fto #30,000 from September.             
OL,15,FThe results of the NEU ballot found    
OL,16,Fthat 98% of members were in favour of  
OL,17,Fturning the deal down.                 
OL,19,FThe education secretary said it was    
OL,20,F"extremely disappointing".             
